description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'Just Go Row' from the channel James Dietz.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Competitor vibe.
The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%. The The Competitor vibe means Gamified, leaderboard-driven, full-send energy. This is especially good for Those who need to chase a score or beat their own record..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: Burst off the line with James as you challenge yourself to hit new speeds together.

Max rhythm: 34, Format: HIIT...
